data.description: Situated in the quiet and well maintained Parklane community, this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath townhouse is an incredible value with tremendous potential. This home greets you with a spacious family room with cozy fireplace and adjacent dining area. The bright kitchen offers generous countertop space including breakfast bar seating and ample storage with pantry. French doors lead you to your private outdoor patio, perfect for relaxing, entertaining and BBQ-ing. One updated guest bathroom along with indoor laundry room complete the downstairs. Upstairs you'll find three bedrooms, spacious bathroom and additional storage space in the hallway. The master bedroom offers its own balcony, great for relaxing, enjoying the surrounding mountain views or catching a sunset. Conveniently located just steps from your front door, you'll find the assigned, covered carport and additional assigned parking space. The community offers well manicured greenbelts and nearby community pool. Nestled within a residential community with plenty of parking and a convenient neighborhood park right next door, this home is wonderful opportunity all around! Welcome home!
